OL,7,FA "one in a million" mother fatally
OL,8,Finjured in the Omagh bomb apologised
OL,9,Fto her husband moments before she
OL,10,Fdied, a public inquiry has heard.
OL,12,FGeraldine Breslin's son Gareth
OL,13,FMcCrystal, speaking publicly about her
OL,14,Fdeath for the first time, told the
OL,15,Finquiry into the 1998 attack that the
OL,16,Fshop worker was "authentic, genuine,
OL,17,Fkind and loved".
