OL,7,FMr McCrystal recalled the horrific
OL,8,Fmoment his stepfather Mark told him
OL,9,Fhis 43-year-old mother, whom he always
OL,10,Fbelieved to be "immortal", had
OL,11,Fsuccumbed in hospital to the severe
OL,12,Finjuries she suffered in the Real IRA
OL,13,Fbombing.
OL,15,FThen 15, the family had decided it was
OL,16,Fbest that Mr McCrystal did not see his
OL,17,Fmother in the hours after the bombing
OL,18,Fas medics battled to save her life.
