OL,7,FWhen her coffin was brought back to
OL,8,Fthe family home in Omagh for a wake it
OL,9,Fwas closed due to the extent of the
OL,10,Finjuries.
OL,12,FMr McCrystal, now 42, told inquiry
OL,13,Fchairman Lord Turnbull that at the
OL,14,Ftime it was "torture" not being able
OL,15,Fto see his mother.
OL,17,FBut he said he has since made peace
OL,18,Fwith the fact, as his final memory of
OL,19,Fher is as she was before the atrocity.
OL,26,@vD@MOUvD@UO]
