OL,7,FMr McCrystal described their
OL,8,Frelationship as "fantastic".
OL,10,F"I adored her," he said.
OL,12,F"I loved her unconditionally, and she
OL,13,Floved me unconditionally. I worshipped
OL,14,Fher.
OL,16,F"We were very, very close. I was her
OL,17,Fonly child and she was very protective
OL,18,Fof me, as any mother is with any child.
OL,20,F"We had a wonderful relationship. She
OL,21,Fwas amazing. She was one in a million.
