OL,7,F"She was an absolute class act, my
OL,8,Fmother."
OL,10,FMr McCrystal added: "What was done to
OL,11,Fher was absolutely despicable and
OL,12,Fappalling.
OL,14,F"My mother was treated by the
OL,15,Fterrorists like she was rubbish, like
OL,16,Fshe was total garbage, and I'd no
OL,17,Fdesire to see my mother battered and
OL,18,Fbloodied and bruised.
