OL,7,FMs Breslin had been working as a shop
OL,8,Fassistant at a local drapery business
OL,9,Fin Omagh on the day of the attack.
OL,11,FShe came home for lunch earlier in the
OL,12,Fday and Mr McCrystal told the inquiry
OL,13,Fhow he had run upstairs to play a
OL,14,Fvideo game after eating and the last
OL,15,Fwords he spoke to his mother were
OL,16,Fcalling downstairs to her as she left
OL,17,Fto go back to work.
