OL,7,FMr McCrystal also recalled the
OL,8,Ffamily's "suffocating and horrible
OL,9,Fexperience" of living out their grief
OL,10,Funder the microscope of the intense
OL,11,Fmedia scrutiny that was focused on the
OL,12,FCo Tyrone town in the aftermath of the
OL,13,Fbombing.
OL,15,FHis mother had raised him, her only
OL,16,Fchild, as a single parent until she
OL,17,Fmet her future husband Mark Breslin in
OL,18,F1993. The couple married in 1995.
