OL,7,FMr McCrystal said his stepfather had
OL,8,Fnever been able to find closure for
OL,9,Fwhat happened on August 15, 1998.
OL,11,F"He was very happy prior to August
OL,12,F1998, very excited for the future he
OL,13,Fand my mother were going to have, and
OL,14,Fthen the bomb ruined everything," he
OL,15,Fsaid.
