OL,7,F"And he hasn't really moved on. He's
OL,8,Ftried his best. He's a very, very
OL,9,Fgood, decent man who didn't ` well,
OL,10,Fnobody deserved this ` but he
OL,11,Fcertainly didn't deserve this to be
OL,12,Fvisited on him. But it's terrible
OL,13,Freally to see him."
OL,15,FTwenty-nine people, including a woman
OL,16,Fpregnant with twins, died in the
OL,17,Fdissident republican bomb attack
OL,18,Fcarried out four months after the
OL,19,Fsigning of Northern Ireland's historic
OL,20,FGood Friday peace accord.
