OL,7,FMr McCrystal reflected on his own
OL,8,Fstruggles in the years after the
OL,9,Fbombing.
OL,11,FHe moved to Birmingham to study in an
OL,12,Feffort to get away from Omagh and the
OL,13,Fmemories of the bombing, but living in
OL,14,FEngland he would go on to develop what
OL,15,Fhe described as a severe drink problem.
OL,17,FMr McCrystal told the inquiry how he
OL,18,Fhas since turned his life around and
OL,19,Fhas been sober for more than 13 years.
OL,21,F"I do have a wonderful life," he said.
