OL,5,Cdying
OL,7,F"I am married and I have three young
OL,8,Fchildren. We have a wonderful
OL,9,Fmarriage, and my kids are amazing and
OL,10,Fwe have a wonderful home and I have a
OL,11,Fgood career.
OL,13,F"I believe I have turned my life
OL,14,Faround. I'm definitely not the angry,
OL,15,Fbitter person I was 15 or 20 years
OL,16,Fago. I think I am a changed man and I
OL,17,Fhave a lot more than most. I think I
OL,18,Fam lucky."
